                    <div>On Thu, Sep 18, 2014 at 8:47 PM,
                      Nick Papior Andersen <span dir="ltr">&lt;<a href="mailto:nickpapior@gmail.com" target="_blank">nickpapior@gmail.com</a>&gt;</span>
